cd shop

# Add product, order, customer schemas
# Create shopping cart Vue islands
# Set up payment processing
# Add admin dashboard
</code></pre>

<h2>Troubleshooting</h2>

<h3>Common Issues</h3>

<strong>"Workspace dependency not found"</strong>
<ul>
<li>Ensure you're running commands inside a Strav workspace</li>
<li>Check that all <code>@strav/*</code> packages are available</li>
</ul>

<strong>"Vue islands not rendering"</strong>
<ul>
<li>Check that <code>@islands</code> directive is in your layout</li>
<li>Verify islands are being built (<code>public/islands.js</code> exists)</li>
<li>Ensure Vue is installed as a dependency</li>
</ul>

<strong>"Database connection failed"</strong>
<ul>
<li>Verify database credentials in <code>.env</code></li>
<li>Ensure your database server is running (PostgreSQL by default)</li>
<li>Check database exists and user has permissions</li>
</ul>

